three leg B-be.CVsim stool under=& stand-D.CS.CVant three string B-be.PPL musical_instrument hand.ADV=& B-insert-CVant chimney-LAT head=& lean.B.CS.CVant sad:FOC musical_instrument play:PLC-CVsim V-sit-CVsim NARP-V 3s mother-room.ADV
