confer+V-LV-INF old father V-be-NEG.PRS 3sRFL.GEN right.ADV+D.NZ false.ADV.NZ.LAT separate-CS.INF old uncle V-be-NEG.PRS 3s:RFL.GEN companion be-INF mother-ERG V-give_birth.PPL brother V-be-NEG.PRS 3s:RFL.GEN alone V-be.PRS 3s:RFL Ingush-PL-DAT among difficult D-be.PRS 3sRFL.DAT say-NW.D 3s.ERG
I don't have an old father to give me advice, I don't have an older uncle to help me tell right from wrong, I don't have a brother to help me, I'm alone in Ingushetia, it's hard for me, he said.

